        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# Recollect \u2014 game-design metrics (\u00a716 in prod)\nBalance metrics from the live match counters. **Seat A = P1 / the opener**, seat B = P2. P1/P2 winrate, draw rate, and PvE (Solace) faction winrate are derived from `recollect_matches_finished_total{result=\"Win(A)\"|\"Win(B)\"|\"Draw\"}` and `recollect_matches_{created,finished}_total{faction=\u2026}`. The **deeper \u00a716 cuts** (winrate-when-leading-at-contraction, evolutions/match, Throughline completion, median match length) are **also live** \u2014 the server's per-match accumulator emits them from the command/event seam (see `docs/observability.md` \u00a72.2). All panels resolve once a few matches have run.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.3.3",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
